      <title>日元反弹威胁日本企业盈利增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/yen-s-rebound-threatens-growth-story-in-japan-earnings-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本企业刚刚公布了创纪录的季度利润，但日元的反弹引发了人们对在中国需求疲软和美国经济放缓风险的情况下，日本企业盈利增长能否持续的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/yen-s-rebound-threatens-growth-story-in-japan-earnings-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 23:21:20 GMT</pubDate>
