    <item>
      <title>道明银行因美国调查遭受 26 亿美元损失，出售嘉信理财股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/td-bank-takes-2-6-billion-hit-on-us-probe-sells-schwab-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多道明银行 (Toronto-Dominion Bank) 拨出 26 亿美元用于支付因其洗钱控制失败而预计支付的罚款，并且该公司出售了其在嘉信理财公司 (Charles Schwab Corp.) 的部分股份来为此提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/td-bank-takes-2-6-billion-hit-on-us-probe-sells-schwab-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 21:17:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告延迟发布，银行却获得了关键就业数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/banks-obtained-key-jobs-revisions-data-while-report-was-delayed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政府的拖延，周三其余华尔街银行不得不等待半个小时，而至少有三家银行成功获得了关键的薪资数据，这导致市场大幅波动，交易部门陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/banks-obtained-key-jobs-revisions-data-while-report-was-delayed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 18:46:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
